Kami memesan kamar hotel untukmu di dekat sini.

247
00:25:46,040 --> 00:25:49,330
Penjepit.

248
00:25:55,510 --> 00:25:56,690
Lagi.

249
00:26:01,070 --> 00:26:02,150
Lagi.

