327
00:34:01,490 --> 00:34:02,780
Berterima kasih?

328
00:34:11,520 --> 00:34:13,470
Kau tidak merendahkan aku?

329
00:34:18,510 --> 00:34:22,270
Oke. Kau boleh pergi.

330
00:34:55,960 --> 00:34:59,060
Bawa pasporku ke Bandara Incheon.

331
