tidak ada penjaga di depan area terbatas.

350
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:24,540
Nona Young Ae sudah tidak disana lagi.

351
00:36:30,530 --> 00:36:31,720
Jepit.

352
00:36:46,690 --> 00:36:47,720
Potong.

353
00:36:50,500 --> 00:36:52,760
